1. *Radilo* je jako hladno prošle noći. (It was very cold last night.)
2. Kada sam *radila* na svojoj doktorskoj disertaciji, nisam imala puno slobodnog vremena. (When I was working on my PhD thesis, I didn't have much free time.)
3. Oni su *radili* cijelu noć kako bi završili projekt na vrijeme. (They worked all night to finish the project on time.)
4. Ja ću *raditi* sve što mogu kako bih pomogao. (I will do everything I can to help.)
5. *Radim* u jednoj uspješnoj IT kompaniji. (I work for a successful IT company.)
6. Kada sam završila fakultet, nisam odmah *radila* u struci. (When I finished college, I didn't immediately work in my field.)
7. Oni *rade* vrlo naporno da bi ostvarili svoje ciljeve. (They work very hard to achieve their goals.)
8. Ja sam *radio* na tom projektu nekoliko mjeseci. (I worked on that project for several months.)
9. Kada *radiš* s ljudima, važno je biti strpljiv i ljubazan. (When you work with people, it's important to be patient and kind.)
10. *Radio* bih nešto drugačije u životu. (I would like to do something different in life.)